      "span_text": "Kerogen acid isolation procedure from cherts Bulk nitrogen isotopic composition (δ 15 NBulk, with respect to the 15 N/ 14 N ratio of the atmospheric N2) was determined on 5 to 10 mg of organic matter (OM) previously isolated through successive demineralisation of ca. 200 g of rocks using hydrofluoric (HF) and hydrochloric (HCl) treatment"
